0for%20connecting%20here%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20it%20because%20people%20are%20outside%20for%20the%20summer.%20Once%20people%20are%20inside%2C%20you're%20barely%20going%20out%2C%20and%20you're%20barely%20going%20to%20connect%20with%20people.%20All%20those%20coffee%20meetups%20and%20%26quot%3Blet's%20go%20get%20drinks%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20done%20for%20the%20dark%20of%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BChicago%20is%20famed%20for%20its%20cold%20winters.%20From%201991%20to%202020%2C%20Chicago%20had%20an%20average%20daily%20maximum%20temperature%20in%20January%20of%2031.6%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%2018.8%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.gov%2Flot%2Ford_rfd_monthly_yearly_normals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENational%20Weather%20Service.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Chicago%20in%20March%202023%2C%20it%20was%20still%20winter%2C%20and%20it%20was%20cold%2C%20so%20there%20really%20wasn't%20a%20lot%20of%20socializing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20got%20a%20little%20bit%20spoiled%20this%20winter%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20Chicagoans%20were%20saying%20this%20winter%20really%20was%20light.%20So%20that%20extended%20the%20social%20season%20a%20little%20bit%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20that%20because%20I%20would%20still%20go%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20new%20year%20hit%2C%20I%20was%20indoors%2C%20I%20was%20not%20doing%20anything.%20I%20live%20by%20myself.%20It%20was%20too%20cold%20to%20even%20think%20to%20leave%20the%20house%2C%20even%20think%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20friends.%20I%20was%20just%20at%20home%20nesting%2C%20enjoying%20my%20own%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20days%20that%20we%20had%20that%20were%20a%20little%20bit%20warmer%20and%20above%20freezing%2C%20I%20was%20making%20an%20effort%20to%20continue%20to%20meet%20peop