uzz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20infighting%20within%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20main%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannauj%20MP's%20remark%20comes%20amid%20the%20buzz%20over%20a%20cryptic%20remark%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya.%20%26quot%3BThe%20organisation%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20government.%20No%20one%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maurya%20said%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20working%20committee.%20The%20remark%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Adityanath.%20Also%2C%20this%20followed%20Mr%20Maurya's%20meeting%20with%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20infighting%20in%20the%20government.%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20fighting%20among%20themselves.%20The%20people%20know%20about%20the%20corruption%20and%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20game%20of%20thrones%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20at%20a%20party%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20been%20put%20on%20the%20back%20burner%20as%20the%20state's%20BJP%20leaders%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20engineered%20splits%20in%20other%20parties%2C%20is%20now%20doing%20the%20same%20within.%20This%20is%20why%20it%20is%20sinking%20in%20the%20quicksand%20of%20infighting.%20There%20is%20no%20one%20in%20the%20BJP%20to%20think%20for%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20buzz%20surrounding%20Mr%20Maurya's%20remark%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20stand%20with%20those%20who%20lost%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Maurya%2C%20a%20former%20UP%20BJP%20chief%2C%20lost%20the%202022%20Assembly%20election%20but%20was%20retained%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%20He%20is%20now%20a%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20BJP%20state%20leaders'%20meet%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%26quot%3B%20cost%20the%20BJP%20dearly%20in%20the%20recently-held%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20results%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20came%20as%20a%20rude%20shock%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20general%20election%2C%20its%20score%20dropping%20from%2062%20in%202019%20to%2033%20this%20time.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20made%20huge%20gains%20to%20bag%2037%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20percentage%20of%20votes%20that%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20BJP%20in%202014%20and%20subsequent%20elections%2C%20BJP%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20getting%20the%20same%20number%20of%20votes%20in%202024%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20shifting%20of%20votes%20and%20overconfidence%20have%20hurt%20our%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20calling%20upon%20party%20workers%20to%20step%20up%20preparations%20for%20the%20bypolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20of%20a%20good%20show%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20the%20upcoming%20bypolls%20to%2010%20Assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20upcoming%20state%20budget%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20says%20we%20are%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20globally.%20And%20UP%20talks%20about%20a%201%20trillion%20dollar%20economy.%20The%20state%20government%20should%20tell%20us%20how%20much%20the%20Centre%20has%20helped%20in%20this%20case.%20The%20government%20in%20Delhi%20must%20put%20out%20the%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20if%20we%20become%20the%20third-largest%20economy%2C%20will%20we%20be%20able%20to%20match%20per%20capital%20income%20in%20developed%20countries%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721208300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fniqosmgo_akhilesh-yadav_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22