0my%20career%20as%20a%20creative%2C%20but%20I've%20since%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20permanent%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20traded%20one%20problem%20for%20another%20moving%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20my%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a0706a8-43d9-44eb-b9b4-b022e134dbc7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20to%20show%20I%20was%20eligible%20for%20a%20Global%20Talent%20Visa%20to%20come%20to%20the%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20is%20linked%20to%20Nigeria%20through%20the%20Commonwealth%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20large%20Nigerian%20community%20here.%20I%20felt%20there%20were%20spaces%20where%20I%20would%20belong.%20I'd%20seen%20other%20Nigerian%20writers%20do%20well%20in%20the%20UK%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20accepted%20into%20some%20master's%20programs%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-coolest-universities-in-the-uk-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-universities-in-the-uk-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etuition%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20financial%20costs%20made%20it%20a%20more%20stressful%20option%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20friends%20suggested%20the%20Global%20Talent%20visa%20for%20skilled%20people%20in%20the%20academic%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20arts%20fields.%20It%20seemed%20like%20a%20good%20option%20with%20a%20viable%20pathway%20to%20getting%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20remain%2C%20where%20you%20can%20live%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-commute-5-hours-hamburg-to-london-not-sustainable-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20long%20as%20you%20like%2C%20and%20the%20opportunity%20for%20my%20creative%20work%20to%20be%20rewarded%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20required%20evidence%20that%20I%20was%20a%20leader%20in%20my%20field%20or%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20one.%20I%20submitted%20reviews%20of%20my%20book%2C%20an%20award%20I'd%20won%20and%20another%20I%20was%20nominated%20for%2C%20and%20letters%20of%20recommendation%20from%20several%20arts%20organizations%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20submitted%20the%20evidence%20to%20The%20Arts%20Council%20England%20and%20paid%20my%20application%20fees.%20After%20getting%20approval%20from%20the%20Arts%20Council%2C%20I%20took%20the%20endorsement%20letter%2C%20receipt%20of%20my%20visa%20fees%20and%20immigration%20surcharge%2C%20and%20my%20passport%20to%20the%20visa%20office%20in%20Lagos.%20My%20application%20was%20approved%20in%20August%2C%20permitting%20me%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20in%20the%20UK%20for%20up%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20renew%20my%20visa%20after%20three%20years%2C%20I'd%20need%20evidence%20that%20I'd%20been%20earning%20money%20from%20my%20line%20of%20work.%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20UK%20indefinitely%2C%20so%20I%20needed%20to%20secure%20relevant%20paid%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22283379ae-1acb-4dec-8460-8c40e8bf1841%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20been%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20paid%20work%20in%20the%20UK's%20creative%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hesitant%20about%20leaving%20everything%20and%20everyone%20I%20loved%20and%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flearn-work-naturally-good-enjoy-career-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarting%20my%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20in%20a%20new%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20in%20Nigeria%20feels%20like%20summer%2C%20but%20I%20landed%20in%20the%20UK%20in%20autumn%2C%20which%20quickly%20transitioned%20to%20winter.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20used%20to%20it%20getting%20dark%20by%204%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saved%20a%20great%20deal%20before%20moving.%20I%20was%20fairly%20comfortable%20with%20the%20income%20from%20my%20full-time%20job%20and%20writing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-side-hustles-for-introverts-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20hustles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20for%20around%20eight%20months%2C%20I%20spent%20less%20than%20a%20third%20of%20my%20salary%20to%20save%20before%20resigning%20from%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20arriving%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I'd%20lined%20up%20part-time%20editing%20work.%20I'd%20been%20vigorously%20applying%20for%20full-time%20employment%20in%20the%20arts%20but%20couldn't%20land%20anything.%20After%20around%20three%20months%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20secured%20a%20full-time%20position%20as%20a%20digital%20marketing%20executive%20for%20a%20power%20tool%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20involves%20some%20copywriting%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK's%20creative%20industry.%20I%20applied%20to%20editing%20and%20contributor%20roles%20but%20got%20rejection%20after%20rejection.%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20freelance%20but%20haven't%20secured%20permanent%20creative%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-to-london-stressful-lonely-now-moving-to-portugal-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon%20was%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20stayed%20with%20a%20friend%20in%20London%20for%20the%20first%20six%20weeks%20before%20moving%20into%20my%20own%20apartment.%20I%20had%20Nigerian%20friends%20who%20lived%20across%20England%2C%20but%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20meet%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20how%20the%20creative%20industry%20worked%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20knowledge%20of%20opportunities%20here%2C%20and%20there's%20only%20so%20much%20you%20can%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nigeria%2C%20I've%20worked%20as%20a%20staff%20writer%20and%20senior%20editor%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20there's%20more%20competition%20for%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20roles%20in%20the%20UK.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20I%20see%20an%20opening%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20100%20people%20will%20have%20applied%20in%20the%20past%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20organizations%20that%20have%20rejected%20me%20have%20said%20they%20want%20candidates%20with%20more%20UK%20experience%2C%20so%20the%20criteria%20seem%20quite%20stringent%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20was%20entering%20a%20senior%20stage%20of%20my%20career%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20but%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20can't%20land%20midlevel%20jobs.%20I've%20seen%20some%20of%20my%20Nigerian%20peers%20apply%20for%20entry-level%20British%20jobs%20who%20were%20at%20a%20mid-senior%20level%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20being%20at%20a%20senior%20level%20in%20Nigeria%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20be%20an%20improvement%20because%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68402662%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20downturn%3C%2Fa%3E%20affects%20people%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fafrica%2Fnigerias-inflation-rises-more-than-27-year-high-december-2024-01-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20is%20soaring%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20struggling%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20return%20to%20Nigeria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22839091e1-1631-4a15-834f-6ef4bc9c0af3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20UK%20isn't%20perfect%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20career%20opportunities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20na%C3%AFve%20when%20I%20first%20arrived.%20Earning%20in%20pounds%20felt%20like%20a%20big%20deal%20because%20of%20the%20exchange%20rate.%20There%20are%20never%20power%20outages%20like%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20safer.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20UK%20is%20not%20perfect.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-cost-of-living-what-is-middle-class-housing-market-2024-4%5C%2