%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%20spoke%20about%20his%20father%20Sham%20Kaushal's%20struggles%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20and%20revealed%20why%20he%20left%20Engineering%20despite%20getting%20good%20marks%20and%20getting%20a%20job%20offer!%20The%20actor%20said%20his%20parents%20were%20very%20happy%20with%20him%20doing%20Engineering%20and%20just%20getting%20a%20good%20job!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-reveals-his-father-sham-kaushal-wanted-to-commit-suicide-when-he-was-jobless-despite-ma-in-english-he-was-ready-to-work-as-a-sweeper-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F111805816.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%201%2C200%20Crore%20Needed%20For%20India's%20Electric%20Car%20Revolution%3A%20Top%20Scientist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20expectation%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Union%20Budget%20is%20enhanced%20incentives%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20India%20is%20the%20global%20capital%20for%20air%20pollution%2C%20and%20e-mobility%20is%20a%20very%20promising%20way%20to%20reduce%20that%2C%20at%20least%20in%20big%20cities.%20India's%20chief%20scientist%20has%20released%20a%20new%20roadmap%20for%20research%20on%20e-mobility%2C%20asserting%20that%20if%20the%20government%20invests%20Rs%201.200%20crore%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20then%20in%20less%20than%20five%20years%2C%20India%20can%20aspire%20to%20lead%20in%20electric%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Sood%2C%20Principal%20Scientific%20Adviser%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20very%20soon%20internal%20combustion%20engines%20running%20on%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20will%20become%20extinct%20like%20dinosaurs%2C%20with%20electric%20vehicles%20becoming%20the%20preferred%20mode%20of%20transportation.%20Professor%20Sood%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%2C%20nearly%209%20lakh%20electric%20vehicles%20were%20sold%20in%20India%2C%20but%20the%20penetration%20has%20to%20go%20up%20to%2030%20per%20cent%20by%202030.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20report%20titled%20%26quot%3Be-Mobility%20R%26amp%3BD%20Roadmap%20for%20India%26quot%3B%20was%20launched%20by%20Professor%20Sood.%20The%20R%26amp%3BD%20roadmap%20has%20been%20prepared%20after%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20global%20automotive%20sector%20and%20identifying%20future%20cutting-edge%20technological%20requirements.%20It%20categorises%20research%20projects%20into%20four%20important%20areas%3A%20energy%20storage%20cells%2C%20electric%20vehicle%20aggregates%2C%20materials%20and%20recycling%2C%20and%20charging%20and%20refuelling%2C%20providing%20clear%20pathways%20to%20attain%20global%20leadership%20by%20being%20Atmanirbhar%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20become%20affordable%20and%20popular%2C%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20is%20really%20required%20in%20battery%20technology.%20Professor%20Sood%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BResearch%20on%20sodium-ion%20batteries%20and%20aluminum-ion%20batteries%20looks%20promising.%26quot%3B%20Making%20cheaper%2C%20lighter%2C%20safer%2C%20and%20longer-lasting%20batteries%20is%20the%20real%20key%20to%20the%20successful%20adoption%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Sood%20highlighted%20that%20India%20aims%20to%20achieve%20a%2045%20per%20cent%20reduction%20in%20emission%20intensity%20by%202030%20and%20energy%20independence%20by%202047%20to%20reach%20net-zero%20commitment%20by%202070.%20A%20significant%20part%20of%20this%20vision%20will%20require%20the%20wider%20adoption%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20indigenous%20energy%20storage%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20generation%20of%20renewable%20energy%20to%20feed%20charging%20infrastructures.%20He%20said%20that%20presently%2C%20the%20e-mobility%20value%20chain%20heavily%20depends%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20e-mobility%20R%26amp%3BD%20roadmap%20charts%20a%20course%20towards%20future%20independence%20and%20self-sufficiency%2C%20outlining%20critical%20research%20initiatives%20that%20will%20position%20India%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20global%20value%20and%20supply%20chains%20within%20the%20next%20five%20to%20seven%20years.%20This%20roadmap%20aims%20to%20fill%20critical%20gaps%20in%20the%20current%20research%20and%20development%20framework.%20While%20many%20identified%20projects%20are%20yet%20to%20achieve%20global%20success%2C%20some%20areas%20already%20demonstrate%20significant%20international%20accomplishments%20and%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20commence%20preparations.%20These%20projects%20are%20included%20to%20establish%20a%20strong%20foundation%20for%20the%20country%20to%20pursue%20future%20innovations%20in%20those%20areas%20when%20opportunities%20arise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Sood%20said%20that%20the%20automobile%20sector%20in%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20contributors%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%2C%20and%20considering%20its%20fast%20growth%20trajectory%2C%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20future.%20He%20emphasized%20that%20this%20progress%20should%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20Net-Zero%20vision%20of%20the%20country%20and%20that%20there%20is%20an%20impending%20need%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20innovation-driven%20growth%20in%20the%20automotive%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Karthick%20Athmanathan%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20report%20and%20Professor%20of%20Practice%20at%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20said%20that%20India%20%26quot%3Bneeded%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20current%20import-dependent%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEasier%20said%20than%20done%2C%20but%20Professor%20Sood%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BBeing%20self-sufficient%20is%20most%20important%2C%20and%20India%20can%20become%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20global%20electric%20vehicle%20supply%20chain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721207880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6qdhcm3o_professor-sood-_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-200-crore-needed-for-indias-electric-car-revolution-top-scientist-6124787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20big%20expectation%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Union%20Budget%20is%20enhanced%20incentives%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20India%20is%20the%20global%20capital%20for%20air%20pollution%2C%20and%20e-mobility%20is%20a%20very%20promising%20way%20to%20reduce%20that%2C%20at%20least%20in%20big%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-200-crore-needed-for-indias-electric-car-revolution-top-scientist-6124787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-200-crore-needed-for-indias-electric-car-revolution-top-scientist-6124787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-200-crore-needed-for-indias-electric-car-revolution-top-scientist-6124787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Massive%20Row%20Over%20Karnataka%20100%25%20Quota%20Bill%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Deletes%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsiddaramaiah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESiddaramaiah%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20deleted%20a%20social%20media%20post%20announcing%20100%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Kannadigas%20in%20all%20Group%20C%20and%20Group%20D%20jobs%20in%20private%20companies%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReservation%20of%20jobs%20in%20private%20firms%20will%20be%20capped%20at%2070%20per%20cent%20for%20non-management%20roles%20and%2050%20per%20cent%20for%20management-level%20employees%2C%20Labour%20Minister%20Santosh%20Lad%20clarified%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20management%20level%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20provide%20reservation%20to%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20people.%20At%20the%20non-management%20level%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20provide%20work%20to%2070%20per%20cent...%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20if%20companies%20were%20unable%20to%20hire%20suitable%20skilled%20candidates%20from%20this%20restricted%20pool%2C%20they%20could%20then%20look%20at%20hiring%20people%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20such%20skills%20are%20not%20available%20(in%20Kannadigas)%20then%20the%20jobs%20can%20be%20outsourced.%20The%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20law%20to%20give%20preference%20to%20locals...%20if%20skilled%20labour%20is%20available%20here...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20declared%20there%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20talent%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BKarnataka%20has%20enough%20skilled%20workforce.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20engineering%20colleges%2C%20medical%20colleges%2C%20international%20schools...%20We%20are%20asking%20them%20to%20give%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20work%20to%20Kannadigas.%20If%20enough%20talent%20is%20not%20available%20they%20can%20bring%20from%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Siddaramaiah%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20posted%20the%20100%20per%20cent%20reservation%20news%20on%20X%20(earlier%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Cabinet%20meeting%20held%20yesterday%20approved%20a%20bill%20to%20make%20recruitment%20of%20100%20per%20cent%20Kannadigas%20mandatory%20for%20'C%20and%20D'%20grade%20posts%20in%20all%20private%20industries%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-okays-bill-mandating-100-quota-for-kannadigas-in-private-firms-for-these-posts-6120407%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Okays%20Bill%20For%20100%25%20Quota%20For%20Locals%20In%20Private%20Firms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20it%20was%20his%20government's%20wish%20Kannadigas%20be%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20lead%20a%20comfortable%20life%20in%20their%20state%20and%20not%20be%20deprived%20of%20jobs%20in%20'Kannada%20land'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BFascist%2C%20Discriminatory%26quot%3B%3A%20Industrialists%20React%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20decision%20was%20not%20well%20received%20by%20business%20leaders%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20said%20the%20IT%20industry%2C%20on%20which%20Bengaluru%20(and%20Karnataka)%20has%20made%20much%20of%20its%20fortune%2C%20would%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20bill%20is%20discriminatory%2C%20regressive...%20this%20is%20a%20fascist%20bill%2C%20as%20in%20'Animal%20Farm'%20(the%20George%20Orwell%20novel)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohandas%20Pai%2C%20Chairman%20of%20Manipal%20Global%20Education%20Services%2C%20had%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiocon%20Executive%20Chairperson%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20was%20more%20circumspect%3B%20she%20welcomed%20the%20proposal%20but%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bcaveats%20that%20exempt%20highly%20skilled%20recruitment%20from%20this%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20tech%20hub%20we%20need%20skilled%20talent%20and%20whilst%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20jobs%20for%20locals%20we%20must%20not%20affect%20our%20leading%20position%20in%20technology%20by%20this%20move.%20There%20must%20be%20caveats%20that%20exempt%20highly%20skilled%20recruitment%20from%20this%20policy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiddaramaiah%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40siddaramaiah%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDKShivakumar%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DKShivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPriyankKharge%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PriyankKharge%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FitYWdHcMWw%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FitYWdHcMWw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20(%40kiranshaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkiranshaw%2Fstatus%2F1813414167191380353%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20tech%20hub%20we%20need%20skilled%20talent%20and%20whilst%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20jobs%20for%20locals%2C%20we%20must%20not%20affect%20our%20leading%20position%20in%20technology%20by%20this%20move.%20There%20must%20be%20a%20caveat...%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mazumdar-Shaw's%20company's%20registered%20office%20is%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Electronics%20City%2C%20an%20800-acre%20industrial%20and%20technology%20hub%20that%20also%20has%20offices%20of%20Infosys%2C%20Wipro%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiocon%2C%20a%20global%20biopharmaceuticals%20enterprise%2C%20employs%20over%2016%2C500%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERK%20Misra%2C%20co-Chairman%20of%20ASSOCHAM%20Karnataka%2C%20called%20the%20proposal%20%26quot%3Bshort-sighted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20genius%20move%20from%20Government%20of%20Karnataka.%20Mandate%20LOCAL%20RESERVATION%20and%20APPOINT%20GOVT%20OFFICER%20IN%20EVERY%20COMPANY%20to%20monitor.%20This%20will%20scare%20(companies)...%20short-sighted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20these%20concerns%2C%20Mr%20Lad%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20he%20would%20speak%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20their%20views.%20We%20will%20talk%20to%20them...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Will%20Resolve...%26quot%3B%20Minister%20On%20Jobs%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20after%20industrialists%20expressed%20their%20concern%2C%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20Minister%20HB%20Patil%20provided%20reassurance%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20that%20many%20people%20have%20apprehensions...%20we%20will%20resolve%20this%20confusion...%20so%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20adverse%20effect...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20need%20for%20all%20states%2C%20not%20just%20Karnataka%2C%20to%20be%20at%20their%20%26quot%3Bpeak%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20competitive%20and%20globalised%20era%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20industrial%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20experiencing%20a%20manufacturing%20and%20industrial%20revolution...%20In%20this%20competitive%20era%2C%20states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Telangana%20are%20striving%20to%20be%20at%20their%20best.%20It%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20for%20all%20states%20to%20be%20at%20their%20competitive%20peak%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20Karnataka%20could%20not%20lose%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-century%20race%20of%20industrialisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka's%20Jobs%20Reservation%20Proposal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrafted%20by%20the%20Labour%20Department%2C%20the%20proposed%20bill%20claimed%20the%20jobs%20in%20question%20were%20being%20given%20largely%20to%20people%20from%20the%20northern%20states%20who%20were%20then%20settling%20in%20Karnataka.%20It%20proposed%20that%20Karnataka-based%20companies%20benefitting%20from%20state-provided%20infrastructure%20reserve%20jobs%20for%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20policy%2C%20it%20is%20understood%2C%20reflected%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20Sarojini%20Mahishi%20Committee%2C%20which%20said%