n%20the%20cold%20months%2C%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-electric-vehicle-add-on-subscriptions-upsells-automakers-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheated%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ensure%20comfort%20year-round.%20The%20heated%20steering%20wheel%20is%20also%20a%20nice%20touch%20and%20adds%20a%20high-quality%20feel%20to%20the%20upscale%20ergonomics%20of%20the%20interior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToyota%20did%20a%20great%20job%20giving%20the%20operators%20a%20wide%20field%20of%20view.%20Passengers%20can%20enjoy%20the%20fixed%20glass%20roof%2C%20which%20offers%20360-degree%20views%20all%20around%20the%20car%2C%20almost%20like%20fishbowl%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoft%20vegan%20leather%20seats%20inside%20make%20it%20very%20comfortable%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle's%20ergonomics%20are%20super%20user-friendly.%20Everything%20in%20the%20Prius%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20because%20the%20JBL%20infotainment%20system%20is%20quite%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22242a533c-2c54-40b3-b8b0-5ee7d89b6800%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDriving%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20experience%20is%20not%20what%20you'd%20expect%20from%20a%20normal%20Prius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20iteration%2C%20Toyota%20continuously%20makes%20the%20Prius%20Prime%20smoother%2C%20quieter%2C%20and%20more%20capable.%20According%20to%20Toyota%2C%20the%202024%20model%20has%20about%2099%20more%20horsepower%20than%20previous%20versions%2C%20so%20it's%20quite%20a%20bit%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20EV%20mode%2C%20the%20acceleration%20feels%20perky%2C%20but%20when%20driving%20as%20a%20hybrid%2C%20it's%20actually%20faster.%20You%20can%20easily%20toggle%20back%20and%20forth%20and%20feel%20the%20Prius%20Prime%20respond%2C%20although%20the%20switchover%20was%20a%20little%20clunky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20put%20the%20Prius%20Prime%20into%20the%20hybrid%20mode%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20drive%20and%20it%20didn't%20seem%20as%20smooth%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20a%20great%20driving%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20offers%20excellent%20range.%20This%20year's%20model%20features%20about%20a%2040-mile%20range%2C%20while%20last%20year's%20had%20about%20a%2025-mile%20range.%20The%20combustion%20engine's%20EPA%20rating%20is%2048%20mpg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prius%20Prime%20XSE%20only%20has%20front-wheel%20drive%2C%20but%20in%20every%20mode%2C%20it's%20very%20quick%20and%20smooth%20to%20drive.%20I%20prefer%20four-wheel%20drive%20for%20safety%20reasons%20because%20I%20live%20somewhere%20hilly%20that%20can%20become%20icy%20in%20the%20cold%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20steering%20gives%20great%20feedback%2C%20so%20you%20know%20exactly%20where%20your%20tires%20are.%20The%2019-inch%20wheels%20are%20slightly%20larger%20than%20average%2C%20making%20it%20a%20fun%20car%20to%20ride%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20new%20vehicle%2C%20I%20would%20absolutely%20buy%20a%20Prius%20Prime.%20It's%20a%20great%20price%20for%20great%20fuel%20efficiency%2C%20with%20comfortable%20seats%20for%20a%205'3%26quot%3B%20person.%20Many%20of%20its%20features%20come%20standard%2C%20but%20I%20might%20even%20spring%20for%20the%20XSE%20Premium%20model%20since%20the%20base%20price%20is%20so%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-toyota-prius-prime-xse-so-nimble-forgot-hybrid-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721207042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696cc108893442a51571f94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-toyota-prius-prime-xse-so-nimble-forgot-hybrid-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202024%20Prius%20Prime%20XSE%20Premium%20model%20comes%20in%20at%20just%20under%20%2440%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20a%20great%20price%20for%20its%20fuel%20efficiency%20and%20power.%22%2C%22a