C000-word%20Republican%20platform%20adopted%20on%20Monday%20by%20the%20party's%20delegates%20which%20makes%20no%20mention%20of%20plans%20for%20climate%20change%20or%20renewable%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20promises%20to%20end%20%26quot%3Bgreen%26quot%3B%20policies%20it%20deems%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20the%20United%20States%20will%20become%20the%20world's%20number%20one%20oil%20and%20natural%20gas%20producer%20--%20a%20position%20it%20already%20holds%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20himself%20has%20said%20he%20is%20opposed%20to%20wind%20power%20--%20a%20widely-touted%20alternative%20to%20fossil%20fuels%20--%20as%20he%20is%20convinced%20it%20%26quot%3Bkills%20all%20the%20birds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Bright%20future'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Sunrise%20Movement%20have%20criticized%20the%20Republican%20platform%2C%20saying%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bhas%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they're%20happy%20to%20make%20the%20climate%20crisis%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Stephen%20Perkins%20of%20the%20American%20Conservation%20Coalition%20--%20perhaps%20the%20only%20booth%20at%20the%20Republican%20convention%20focused%20on%20preserving%20the%20planet%20--%20you%20have%20to%20take%20Trump's%20comments%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20grain%20of%20salt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20some%20of%20his%20comments%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20more%20entertaining%20than%20policy%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20wearing%20a%20striped%20blue%20polo%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20organization%20is%20hoping%20to%20show%20what%20a%20%26quot%3Bconservative%20approach%20to%20environmental%20policy%20and%20climate%20policy%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20thinks%20could%20entice%20younger%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20concedes%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bslow%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20older%20Republicans%20averse%20to%20agreeing%20to%20action%20on%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Yale%20survey%20published%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20Americans%20do%20believe%20in%20the%20existence%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20does%20not%20necessarily%20translate%20into%20support%20for%20Democratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20pushed%20through%20several%20initiatives%20to%20combat%20global%20warming%20during%20his%20time%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerkins%20instead%20believes%20Biden%20is%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bradical%20sect%26quot%3B%20of%20progressives%20%26quot%3Bthat%20doesn't%20engage%20in%20nuance.%26quot%3B%20His%20convention%20stand%20shows%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bdestruction%26quot%3B%20alongside%20images%20of%20left-wing%20environmental%20activists%20throwing%20soup%20at%20a%20work%20of%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20had%20it%20his%20way%2C%20he%20would%20show%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20a%20bright%20future%20ahead%26quot%3B%20despite%20the%20challenges%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20doom%20and%20gloom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721206740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F4d8nnee8_donald-trump-1200_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrumps-fossil-fuel-agenda-gets-priority-over-climate-change-at-convention-6124272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Climate%20change%20is%20little%20more%20than%20an%20afterthought%20for%20attendees%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%2C%20who%20are%20gathered%20this%20week%20to%20crown%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20their%20party's%20nominee%20for%20this%20