024-07%2Flhgqt1s_deepfake_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20actors%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Anushka%20Sharma%20and%20Shilpa%20Shetty%2C%20cricketer%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE)%20MD%20and%20CEO%20Ashishkumar%20Chauhan%2C%20and%20Indian%20industrialists%20Ratan%20Tata%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20have%20in%20common%3F%20They've%20all%20been%20targets%20of%20deepfake%20videos%20that%20used%20their%20personas%20to%20peddle%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20and%20medication%20for%20diabetes%2C%20and%20promote%20fraudulent%20money-making%20schemes%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERapid%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20have%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20technological%20disruption%2C%20with%20deepfakes%20emerging%20as%20a%20particularly%20concerning%20challenge%20for%20India's%20information%20integrity%20and%20public%20discourse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Misinformation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20buildup%20to%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20significant%20numbers%20of%20people%20in%20India%20had%20already%20been%20targeted%20by%20audio%20and%20audio-visual%20deepfakes%2C%20although%20these%20were%20mainly%20attempts%20to%20scam%20them%20in%20various%20ways.%20Around%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20were%20also%20initial%20fears%20that%20political%20deepfakes%20could%20be%20used%20to%20try%20to%20influence%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20fears%20were%20only%20justified%20when%20the%20election%20campaign%20got%20underway.%20Fake%20clips%20showing%20Bollywood%20actors%20Aamir%20Khan%20and%20Ranveer%20Singh%20criticising%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20were%20circulated%20widely.%20However%2C%20ultimately%2C%20it%20may%20be%20said%20that%20while%20there%20were%20instances%20of%20deepfakes%20being%20used%20for%20mudslinging%2C%20targeted%20political%20attacks%20and%20even%20spreading%20misinformation%20about%20exit%20polls%2C%20parties%20used%20technology%20largely%20for%20their%20own%20voter%20outreach%20and%20engagement%20and%20to%20overcome%20language%20barriers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%20were%20also%20used%20by%20parties%20to%20'resurrect'%20their%20dead%20leaders%20to%20enhance%20the%20emotional%20connection%20with%20voters.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20an%20AI-generated%20voice%20message%20from%20former%20chief%20minister%20J.%20Jayalalithaa%2C%20who%20died%20in%202016%2C%20was%20circulated%20to%20criticise%20the%20current%20governing%20party%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK).%20The%20DMK%20in%20turn%20used%20AI-generated%20videos%20of%20their%20own%20deceased%20leader%2C%20M.%20Karunanidhi%2C%20to%20praise%20his%20son%20and%20current%20chief%20minister%2C%20M.K.%20Stalin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheapfakes%20vs%20Deepfakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20risk%20posed%20by%20AI-generated%20content%20during%20the%20elections%20wasn't%20as%20deep%20as%20expected%2C%20even%20edited%20videos%20were%20often%20misattributed%20as%20AI-generated%20or%20%26quot%3Bdeepfake%26quot%3B%20content.%20For%20instance%2C%20an%20edited%20video%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20that%20was%20circulated%20before%20the%20polls%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20he%20promised%20to%20scrap%20reservations%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20if%20elected.%20While%20the%20clip%20was%20edited%20using%20simple%20video%20editing%20tools%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20several%20mainstream%20media%20organisations%20mislabelled%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeepfake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20deepfakes%20are%20AI-generated%20media%20created%20using%20machine%20learning%20algorithms%20that%20can%20map%20one%20person's%20face%20onto%20another's%20body%2C%20and%20even%20alter%20their%20speech.%20Creating%20such%20media%20requires%20significant%20computational%20power.%20In%20contrast%2C%20'cheapfakes'%20are%20manipulated%20media%20created%20using%20relatively%20simple%20editing%20tools.%20They%20are%20less%20sophisticated%20than%20deepfakes%20but%20can%20still%20effectively%20spread%20misinformation.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20used%20widely%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20India%20Should%20Do%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20detection%20algorithms%20for%20deepfakes%20to%20media%20literacy%20for%20cheapfakes%2C%20India%20can%20and%20should%20develop%20more%20targeted%20countermeasures%20for%20the%20various%20kinds%20of%20manipulated%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20which%20was%20once%20a%20complex%20and%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20has%20increasingly%20become%20very%20accessible.%20The%20turnaround%20time%20has%20reduced%20from%20days%20to%20minutes%2C%20even%20seconds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20rapid%20evolution%20in%20technology%20poses%20a%20significant%20challenge%20for%20fact-checkers%20and%20content%20moderators%2C%20who%20struggle%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20pace%20of%20misinformation.%20Fact-checkers%20in%20India%20have%20found%20it%20an%20uphill%20battle%20to%20debunk%20deepfake%20content%20when%20it%20is%20spread%20at%20speed%20and%20scale%20or%20during%20heightened%20activity%2C%20such%20as%20election%20seasons.%20The%20disparity%20in%20the%20speed%20of%20information%20dissemination%20underscores%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20more%20efficient%20and%20streamlined%20verification%20processes.%20A%20multifaceted%20approach%20is%20required%20to%20safeguard%20the%20integrity%20of%20its%20democratic%20processes.%20This%20approach%20must%20encompass%20technological%20advancements%2C%20regulatory%20frameworks%2C%20and%20a%20shift%20in%20societal%20mindsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Way%20Ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20deepfakes%20have%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20detect%2C%20developing%20AI-powered%20tools%20to%20identify%20and%20counter%20such%20manipulated%20content%20holds%20promise.%20Tech%20giants%20like%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20have%20pledged%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20voters%20to%20protect%20access%20to%20truthful%20information.%20However%2C%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20currently%20proposed%20measures%2C%20such%20as%20labelling%20and%20watermarking%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinued%20innovation%20and%20collaboration%20in%20this%20domain%20is%20paramount.%20By%20leveraging%20AI-powered%20tools%2C%20fact-checkers%20and%20content%20moderators%20can%20expedite%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20discover%20false%20claims%2C%20pre-empt%20them%20before%20they%20cause%20harm%20and%2C%20in%20time%2C%20even%20automate%20deepfake%20detection%2C%20freeing%20up%20valuable%20human%20resources%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20nuanced%20and%20contextual%20analysis.%20This%20shift%20in%20mindset%2C%20from%20viewing%20AI%20as%20the%20ultimate%20verifier%20to%20understanding%20its%20role%20in%20supporting%20human%20verification%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20more%20efficient%20and%20effective%20strategies%20for%20combating%20deepfake-driven%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deepfakes%20Analysis%20Unit%20(DAU)%20initiative%2C%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20collaboration%20of%20academics%2C%20researchers%2C%20startups%2C%20tech%20platforms%2C%20and%20fact-checkers%2C%20is%20an%20example%20of%20notable%20efforts%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFostering%20a%20media-literate%20population%20is%20also%20crucial%20to%20counter%20deepfakes.%20Educating%20the%20public%20about%20the%20risks%20and%20the%20need%20to%20verify%20information%20can%20empower%20them%20to%20navigate%20digital%20content%20with%20scepticism%20and%20resilience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20Others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Indian%20government's%20initial%20reluctance%20to%20regulate%20AI%20seems%20to%20be%20ebbing%20as%20technology's%20potential%20for%20misuse%20becomes%20clearer.%20Recently%2C%20following%20a%20controversy%20over%20Google's%20Gemini%20chatbot%2C%20the%20government%20issued%20an%20advisory%20that%20reminded%20intermediaries%20to%20take%20action%20against%20AI-generated%20content%20that%20violates%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20Rules%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20spread%20of%20patently%20false%20or%20untrue%20information.%20The%20advisory%20also%20states%20that%20where%20software%20allows%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20it%20should%20also%20label%20or%20embed%20the%20content%20with%20unique%20identifying%20data%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20determine%20how%20the%20content%20was%20created%2C%20and%20by%20which%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deepfake%20challenge%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20India%3B%20it%20is%20a%20global%20phenomenon%20that%20requires%20a%20coordinated%20international%20response.%20The%20European%20Union%20will%20seek%20to%20regulate%20high-risk%20AI%20systems%20through%20its%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Act.%20The%20UK%2C%20too%2C%20has%20tasked%20its%20regulators%20with%20developing%20rules%20for%20various%20sectors%20and%20use-cases.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20may%20also%20issue%20guidance%20on%20labelling%20and%20watermarking%20deep%20fakes%20and%20develop%20standards%20for%20red-teaming%20AI%20models%2C%20which%20can%20have%20multiple%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20ought%20to%20develop%20a%20unique%20framework%20that%20suits%20its%20information%20environment.%20This%20can%20not%20only%20effectively%20counter%20the%20use%20of%20harmful%20deepfakes%20but%20also%20protect%20free%20speech%20and%20useful%20innovation%20(like%20developing%20generative%20AI%20tools%20that%20can%20help%20address%20language%20barriers).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20Drop%20the%20Guard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2086%25%20of%20Indians%20who%20were%20surveyed%20recently%20said%20that%20they%20believe%20misinformation%20and%20deepfakes%20will%20impact%20future%20elections%20and%20that%20candidates%20should%20be%20stopped%20from%20using%20generative%20AI%20in%20their%20promotional%20content.%20While%20the%20risk%20has%20not%20become%20as%20pronounced%20for%20now%2C%20the%20steady%20proliferation%20of%20deepfake%20videos%20of%20celebrities%2C%20industrialists%2C%20and%20news%20anchors%20promoting%20false%20medical%20and%20financial%20solutions%20shows%20the%20technology's%20potential%20for%20perpetuating%20financial%20fraud.%20Amid%20this%2C%20the%20exploitation%20of%20ordinary%20citizens%20remains%20a%20primary%20concern.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20navigate%20this%20challenge%2C%20India%20must%20embrace%20AI's%20potential%20to%20streamline%20the%20verification%20process.%20By%20learning%20from%20global%20best%20practices%2C%20India%20can%20safeguard%20the%20democratic%20foundations%20of%20its%20elections%20and%20empower%20its%20citizens%20to%20navigate%20the%20digital%20landscape%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jaskirat%20Singh%20Bawa%20leads%20editorial%20operations%20at%20Logically%20Facts%2C%20an%20independent%2C%20IFCN-accredited%20fact-checking%20organisation%20that%20operates%20in%2012%20countries%20and%2016%20languages%20globally.%20It%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20AI%20company%20Logically.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721202780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Flnl74qk_deepfake_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-misinformation-to-fraud-the-alarming-rise-of-deepfakes