an%20Memorial%20Hospital%20is%20dated%20August%2024%2C%202022.%20It%20mentions%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20address%20as%20%26quot%3BPlot%20No%2053%2C%20Dehu%20Alandi%20Road%2C%20Talawade%2C%20Pimpri%20Chinchwad%26quot%3B%20in%20Pune%20district.%20But%20at%20this%20location%2C%20there%20is%20no%20house%2C%20but%20a%20factory%20named%20Thermoverta%20Engineering%20Company.%20Interestingly%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20Audi%20car%2C%20which%20has%20been%20seized%20after%20she%20illegally%20used%20a%20red-blue%20beacon%20on%20it%2C%20is%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20this%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20while%20the%20government%20has%20mandated%20Aadhaar%20for%20getting%20disability%20certificates%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20certificate%20mentions%20that%20the%20document%20she%20produced%20was%20a%20ration%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20certificate%20states%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20case%20of%20Locomotor%20Disability%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiagnosis%20in%20her%20case%20is%20Old%20ACL%20tear%20with%20left%20knee%20instability%26quot%3B.%20This%20means%20an%20injury%20in%20the%20Anterior%20Cruciate%20Ligament%20--%20one%20of%20the%20ligaments%20that%20helps%20stabilise%20the%20knee%20joint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar's%20certificate%20mentions%20extent%20of%20disability%20as%207%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Big%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disability%20certificate%20raises%20questions%20on%20how%20Ms%20Khedkar%20managed%20to%20get%20relaxations%20during%20her%20civil%20service%20selection.%20The%2032-year-old%20had%20sought%20relaxation%20under%20%26quot%3Bperson%20with%20benchmark%20disability%26quot%3B%20category.%20But%20UPSC%20rules%20identify%20a%20%26quot%3Bperson%20with%20benchmark%20disability%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20with%20%26quot%3Bnot%20less%20than%20forty%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20disability.%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20certificate%20mentions%20the%20extent%20of%20her%20disability%20as%207%20per%20cent%2C%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20UPSC%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20she%20had%20skipped%20multiple%20appointments%20in%20Delhi%20for%20medical%20check-up%20to%20verify%20her%20disability%20certificate%20and%20then%20submitted%20a%20report%20from%20a%20private%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20of%20the%20Commissioner%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%2C%20Pune%2C%20has%20now%20asked%20police%20to%20check%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20certificates%20submitted%20by%20Ms%20Khedkar.%20The%20Centre%2C%20too%2C%20has%20started%20an%20investigation%20to%20verify%20her%20candidature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20It%20All%20Began%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuja%20Khedkar's%20troubles%20started%20last%20month%20when%20Pune%20collector%20Dr%20Suhas%20Diwase%20wrote%20to%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sujata%20Saunik%2C%20flagging%20many%20demands%20by%20the%202023-batch%20trainee%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20cabin%2C%20a%20car%2C%20residential%20quarters%20and%20a%20peon%20before%20she%20joined%20work%20at%20the%20collectorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collector%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20she%20is%20on%20a%20two-year%20probation%20and%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20these%20benefits.%20Ms%20Khedkar%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20removing%20the%20nameplate%20of%20a%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20collector's%20office%20when%20he%20was%20on%20leave.%20Amid%20the%20row%2C%20she%20was%20transferred%20to%20Washim%20as%20a%20supernumerary%20assistant%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20of%20unreasonable%20demands%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20can%20of%20worms%20as%20her%20selection%20for%20civil%20service%20came%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20authorities%20at%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20put%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20training%20on%20hold%20and%20recalled%20her%20for%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fightback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20has%20alleged%20a%20media%20trial%20against%20her%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Btruth%20will%20come%20out%26quot%3B%20after%20she%20presents%20her%20case%20before%20the%20probe%20commitee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20testify%20before%20the%20committee.%20I%20think%20whatever%20decision%20the%20committee%20will%20take%20should%20be%20acceptable%20to%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20media%20recently.%20The%20Constitution%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20are%20innocent%20until%20proven%20guilty.%20%26quot%3BSo%20proving%20me%20guilty%20by%20media%20trial%20is%20wrong%20on%20everybody's%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20filed%20a%20complaint%20of%20harassment%20against%20Pune%20district%20collector%20Suhas%20Diwase%2C%20who%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20flagging%20her%20alleged%20demands%20for%20perks.%20This%20complaint%20has%20been%20forwarded%20to%20Pune%20Police%2C%20but%20an%20FIR%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721200800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fqee7i53o_puja-khedkar_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-upsc-in-puja-khedkars-disability-certificate-a-factory-address-many-questions-6123837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20addition%20to%20the%20series%20of%20revelations%20in%20the%20row%20surrounding%20trainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20questions%20are%20now%20being%20raised%20on%20a%20disability%20certificate%20issued%20to%20her%20by%20a%20Pune%20hospital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-ups