2%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721200068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111802450%2Cimgsize-175666.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fweb-stories%2Ftamannaah-bhatia-shines-in-vintage-glam-at-anant-radhikas-mangal-utsav%2Fphotostory%2F111802450.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111802450.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETamannaah%20Bhatia%20shines%20in%20vintage%20glam%20at%20Anant-Radhika's%20Mangal%20Utsav%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fweb-stories%2Ftamannaah-bhatia-shines-in-vintage-glam-at-anant-radhikas-mangal-utsav%2Fphotostory%2F111802450.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBizarre%20Reason%26quot%3B%20Why%20No%20Sniper%20Was%20On%20Roof%20Where%20Trump%20Shooter%20Was%20Hiding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Secret%20Service%20is%20facing%20intense%20scrutiny%20after%20a%20shooter%20opened%20fire%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%2C%20and%20questions%20have%20emerged%20about%20why%20no%20sniper%20team%20was%20positioned%20on%20the%20building%20from%20which%20the%20shots%20were%20fired.%20Secret%20Service%20Director%20Kimberly%20Cheatle%20has%20attributed%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20sniper%20team%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bsloped%20roof%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20building%2C%20citing%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Ftrump-rally-shooting-unacceptable-secret-service-director-abc-exclusive%2Fstory%3Fid%3D111962314%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Cheatle%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20building%20in%20particular%20has%20a%20sloped%20roof%20at%20its%20highest%20point.%20And%20so%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there's%20a%20safety%20factor%20that%20would%20be%20considered%20there%20that%20we%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20put%20somebody%20up%20on%20a%20sloped%20roof.%20The%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20secure%20the%20building%20from%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooter%2C%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%2C%20had%20a%20clear%20line%20of%20sight%20of%20Trump%20from%20the%20roof%2C%20which%20was%20approximately%20130%20yards%20away.%20Using%20an%20AR-style%20semi-automatic%20rifle%2C%20Crooks%20opened%20fire%2C%20injuring%20Trump%20and%20two%20others%2C%20and%20killing%20firefighter%20Corey%20Comperatore.%20Secret%20Service%20snipers%20ultimately%20killed%20Crooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20acknowledging%20the%20agency's%20missteps%2C%20Cheatle%20refused%20to%20step%20down%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20that%20shouldn't%20happen%20again.%20The%20buck%20stops%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20spurred%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%20toward%20the%20Secret%20Service%20for%20failing%20to%20fulfil%20its%20%26quot%3Bno%20fail%26quot%3B%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20high-profile%20figures.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20the%20agency's%20handling%20of%20the%20shooting%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20Republican%20leaders%20in%20Congress%20have%20also%20called%20for%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20questions%20remain%20about%20the%20safety%20roles%20at%20the%20rally%20and%20why%20the%20roof%20used%20by%20Crooks%20was%20not%20secured.%20Cheatle%20noted%20that%20the%20building%20where%20the%20shooter%20was%20located%20was%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bouter%20perimeter%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20rally%2C%20which%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20local%20police.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20local%20police%20in%20that%20building%20--%20there%20was%20local%20police%20in%20the%20area%20that%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20outer%20perimeter%20of%20the%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20though%20she%20did%20not%20clarify%20how%20the%20shooter%20was%20able%20to%20access%20the%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20has%20prompted%20the%20Secret%20Service%20to%20vow%20full%20cooperation%20with%20the%20independent%20review.%20Cheatle%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Service%20is%20working%20with%20all%20involved%20federal%2C%20state%2C%20and%20local%20agencies%20to%20understand%20what%20happened%2C%20how%20it%20happened%2C%20and%20how%20we%20can%20prevent%20an%20incident%20like%20this%20from%20ever%20taking%20place%20again.%20We%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20independent%20review%20announced%20by%20President%20Biden%20yesterday%20and%20will%20participate%20fully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%2C%20held%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20was%20interrupted%20when%20multiple%20gunshots%20rang%20out.%20Trump%2C%20visibly%20injured%20with%20blood%20on%20his%20ear%20and%20cheek%2C%20was%20swiftly%20surrounded%20by%20Secret%20Service%20agents%20and%20rushed%20to%20safety.%20The%20shooter%20and%20a%20bystander%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20two%20spectators%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewly%20surfaced%20video%20supports%20witness%20reports%20that%20they%20had%20alerted%20police%20to%20the%20shooter%20on%20the%20roof.%20According%20to%20the%20Washington%20Post%2C%20shots%20targeting%20Trump%20were%20fired%2086%20seconds%20after%20the%20first%20attempts%20to%20warn%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20Biden%20has%20ordered%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20security%20at%20the%20rally%20and%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20where%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20party's%20presidential%20nominee.%20Additionally%2C%20Secret%20Service%20protection%20has%20been%20extended%20to%20independent%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20