oodle%20stand%20and%20was%20heading%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2032-year-old%2C%20realising%20that%20the%20car%20was%20not%20slowing%20down%2C%20tried%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20way%20but%20didn't%20stand%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hitting%20Sidharth%20Sharma%2C%20the%20Mercedes%20went%20over%20a%20pavement%20and%20came%20to%20a%20stop%20as%20its%20front%20tyres%20burst.%20The%20teenager%20abandoned%20the%20car%20and%20ran%20away%20with%20his%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20granted%20the%20insurance%20company%20the%20liberty%20to%20recover%20the%20compensation%20amount%20from%20the%20father's%20company%2C%20on%20which%20name's%20the%20vehicle%20was%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20detailed%20accident%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20police%2C%20the%20minor%20was%20driving%20the%20car%20rashly%20at%20a%20very%20high%20speed.%20After%20the%20collision%2C%20Sidharth%20was%20thrown%2020%20feet%20high%20into%20the%20air%20after%20the%20car%20hit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721198160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fmercedes-cctv-footage_650x400_51459999458.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsidharth-sharma-mercedes-hit-and-run-2016-mercedes-hit-and-run-victims-parents-awarded-rs-1-98-crore-relief-6123642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20insurance%20company%20has%20been%20directed%20by%20the%20Motor%20Accident%20Claim%20Tribunal%20(MACT)%20to%20pay%20about%20Rs%201.98%20crore%20compensation%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20a%2032-year-old%20man%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20hit-and-run%20involving%20a%20minor%20in%202016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsidharth-sharma-mercedes-hit-and-run-2016-mercedes-hit-and-run-victims-parents-awarded-rs-1-98-crore-relief-6123642%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.or