0at%20his%20home%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%20The%20incident%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20place%20at%20the%20former%20cricketer's%20Kanda%20Mawatha%20residence%20in%20Ambalangoda.%20Several%20local%20media%20reports%20have%20suggested%20that%20Niroshana%20was%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20at%20home%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20The%20person%20who%20killed%20Niroshana%20reportedly%20used%20a%2012-bore%20firearm.%20After%20coming%20to%20know%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20police%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20have%20sent%20the%20body%20for%20autopsy.%20No%20further%20information%20is%20yet%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20former%20Sri%20Lankan%20U19%20captain%20reportedly%20shot%20dead%20in%20Ambalangoda.%20Gone%20too%20soon%20brother.%20Discipline%20is%20number%201%20in%20any%20profession.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5QseJBpXJO%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5QseJBpXJO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amila%20Kalugalage%20(%40akalugalage)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fakalugalage%2Fstatus%2F1813260706898452956%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiroshana%20was%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20pace%20bowling%20all-rounders%20to%20have%20come%20out%20of%20Sri%20Lanka's%20youth%20system.%20During%20age-group%20cricket%2C%20he%20said%20to%20have%20led%20the%20likes%20of%20Farvez%20Maharoof%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Angelo%20Mathews%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1260-angelo-mathews-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAngelo%20Mathews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Upul%20Tharanga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F724-upul-tharanga-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUpul%20Tharanga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc.%20He%20quit%20the%20sport%20at%20the%20age%20of%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiroshana%20played%20a%20total%20of%2012%20first-class%20games%20and%208%20List%20A%20matches%20for%20the%20Galle%20Cricket%20Club%20between%202001%20and%202004.%20A%20fine%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20could%20deliver%20with%20both%20the%20bat%20and%20the%20ball%2C%20Niroshana%20scored%20more%20than%20300%20runs%20and%20picked%20up%2019%20wickets%20during%20his%20active%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20his%20debut%20for%20the%20Sri%20Lanka's%20U19%20side%20in%202000%20and%20also%20featured%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20under-19%20Tests%20and%20ODI%20for%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721197560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhbivn9og_niroshan-sri-lanka_625x300_17_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsri-lankas-former-u19-captain-dhammika-niroshana-shot-dead-6123723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20place%20at%20the%20former%20cricketer's%20Kanda%20Mawatha%20residence%20in%20Ambalangoda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsri-lankas-former-u19-captain-dhammika-niroshana-shot-dead-6123723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsri-lankas-former-u19-captain-dhammika-niroshana-shot-dead-6123723%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsri-lankas-former-u19-captain-dhammika-niroshana-shot-dead-6123723%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2225%2C000%20Aspirants%20For%20Airport%20Jobs%20Paying%20Rs%2022%2C000%3A%20A%20Mumbai%20Stampede%20Scare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20airport%20loaders%20led%20to%20a%20stampede-like%20situation%20at%20Mumbai%20airport%20yesterday.%20More%20than%2025%2C000%20applicants%20turned%20up%20for%20a%20shot%20at%20the%202%2C216%20vacancies%2C%20and%20the%20staff%20of%20Air%20India%20Airport%20Services%20Limited%20struggled%20to%20manage%20the%20massive%20crowd.%20Air%20India%20Airport%20Services%20Limited%20provides%20ground%20handling%20services%20at%20major%20airports%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20showed%20the%20applicants%20jostling%20with%20each%20other%20to%20reach%20the%20form%20counters.%20Reports%20said%20the%20applicants%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20without%20food%20and%20water%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20started%20feeling%20unwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirport%20loaders%20are%20tasked%20with%20loading%20and%20unloading%20luggage%20on%20aircraft%20and%20operating%20baggage%20belts%20and%20ramp%20tractors.%20Each%20aircraft%20needs%20at%20least%20five%20loaders%20to%20handle%20luggage%2C%20cargo%20and%20food%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20salary%20of%20airport%20loaders%20ranges%20between%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20but%20most%20make%20over%20Rs%2030%2C000%20after%20overtime%20allowances.%20Educational%20criteria%20for%20the%20job%20are%20basic%2C%20but%20the%20candidate%20must%20be%20physically%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20aspirants%20is%20Prathameshwar%20from%20Buldhana%20district%2C%20who%20has%20travelled%20over%20400%20km%20for%20the%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20post%20of%20handyman.%20They%20are%20offering%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2022%2C500%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Prathameshwar%20is%20a%20second%20year%20BBA%20student.%20Asked%20if%20he%20would%20quit%20his%20studies%20if%20he%20gets%20the%20job%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20we%20do%3F%20There%20is%20so%20much%20unemployment.%20I%20urge%20the%20government%20to%20create%20more%20job%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspirant%20who%20has%20BA%20degree%20said%20he%20does%20not%20know%20much%20about%20the%20work%20of%20a%20handyman%2C%20but%20says%20he%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20the%20job%26quot%3B.%20Another%20candidate%20has%20travelled%20from%20Rajasthan's%20Alwar%20to%20Mumbai.%20He%20has%20an%20MCom%20degree%2C%20but%20has%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20that%20has%20a%20basic%20education%20requirement.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20preparing%20for%20government%20job%20exams%20as%20well%2C%20someone%20told%20me%20that%20the%20salary%20here%20is%20good.%20So%20I%20have%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20incident%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20viral%20video%20showed%20hundreds%20of%20jobseekers%20pushing%20and%20shoving%20each%20other%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-job-video-gujarat-unemployment-video-railing-collapses-as-1-800-aspirants-turn-up-for-10-jobs-in-gujarat-6084232%5C%22%3Ewalk-in%20interview%20at%20Ankleshwar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gujarat's%20Bharuch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%201%2C800%20aspirants%20had%20turned%20up%20for%20a%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20just%2010%20posts%20in%20a%20private%20firm.%20Such%20was%20the%20rush%20that%20a%20railing%20on%20the%20ramp%20leading%20to%20the%20office's%20entry%20collapsed%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20jobseekers.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20ramp%20was%20not%20very%20high%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20aspirants%20who%20lost%20their%20balance%20after%20the%20railing%20collapsed%20suffered%20serious%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8lg57pl8_bharuch-job-interview_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatching%20on%20to%20the%20video%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bexposed%20the%20BJP's%20Gujarat%20model%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20ruling%20party%20was%20imposing%20this%20model%20of%20unemployment%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20BJP%20MP%20Mansukh%20Vasava%20blamed%20the%20private%20firm%20for%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20filling%20up%20only%2010%20vacancies%20and%20should%20have%20specified%20the%20criteria%20properly%20instead%20of%20holding%20an%20open%20interview.%20At%20some%20level%2C%20the%20incident%20occurred%20because%20of%20the%20company.%20We%20are%20worried%20about%20it%20and%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20airport%20video%2C%20too%2C%20has%20prompted%20Congress%20MP%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20to%20raise%20the%20unemployment%20issue%20and%20target%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20unemployment%20situation%20has%20become%20so%20bad%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20that%20youngsters%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20wars%20for%20Russia%20and%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20they%20hear%20of%20jobs%2C%20they%20gather%20in%20thousands%20and%20there%20is%20a%20fear%20of%20stampede%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721197260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9vnumc7o_mumbai-airport_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F25-000-aspirants-for-airport-jobs-paying-rs-22-000-a-mumbai-stampede-scare-6122988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20airport%20loaders%20led%20to%20a%20stampede-like%20situation%20at%20Mumbai%20airport%20yesterday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F25-000-aspirants-for-airport-jobs-paying-rs-22-000-a-mumbai-stampede-scare-6122988%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F25-000-aspirants-for-airport-jobs-paying-rs-22-000-a-mumbai-stampede-scare-61