er%20UBS.%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20UK%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20will%20see%20a%20decline%20in%20millionaires%20by%202028%2C%20per%20a%20new%20UBS%20report.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoth%20countries%20saw%20an%20influx%20of%20millionaires%20from%20people%20choosing%20to%20move%20there.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20millionaire%20decline%20continues%20a%20larger%20trend%20of%20nomadic%20wealth%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20per%20UBS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20developed%20countries%20are%20set%20to%20gain%20more%20wealthy%20people%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20with%20two%20big%20outliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20tracked%2056%20countries%20for%20its%20annual%20wealth%20report%2C%20released%20last%20week.%20The%20financial%20services%20firm%20found%20that%2052%20of%20them%20will%20add%20millionaires%20by%202028.%20Some%20countries%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-new-millionaires-tsmc-ai-semiconductor-chip-ubs-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20will%20gain%20as%20many%20as%2050%25%20more%20millionaires%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20make%20%26quot%3Bnotable%20exceptions%26quot%3B%20on%20this%20list%2C%20per%20UBS%2C%20because%20both%20are%20forecasted%20to%20lose%20millionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20had%20attracted%20%26quot%3Bnomadic%20wealth%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20chose%20to%20move%20to%20those%20countries%2C%20rather%20than%20those%20who%20made%20their%20money%20locally%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20Paul%20Donovan%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWealth%20has%20become%20more%20mobile%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20as%20a%20function%20of%20numerous%20push%20and%20pull%20factors%2C%26quot%3B%20Donovan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20more%20millionaires%20are%20changing%20location%2C%20then%20those%20economies%20which%20are%20disproportionately%20attractive%20for%20nomadic%20wealth%20are%20also%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20movements%20in%20that%20nomadic%20wealth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20three%20million%20millionaires%20put%20it%20third%20among%20countries%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20millionaires%20last%20year%2C%20as%20measured%20in%20US%20dollars%2C%20per%20UBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20%26quot%3Bmore%20millionaires%20than%20there%20should%20be%2C%20given%20the%20size%20of%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Donovan%20said%20at%20a%20media%20event%20on%20July%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20UBS%20forecasts%20this%20number%20to%20decline%20by%2017%25%20by%202028.%20The%20loss%20continues%20a%20trend%3A%20The%20UK%20lost%2016%2C500%20millionaires%20between%202017%20and%202023%2C%20per%20immigration%20consultancy%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners.%20Some%20millionaires%20have%20been%20leaving%20the%20UK%20in%20search%20of%20better%20taxes%20and%20more%20stable%2C%20business-friendly%20politics%2C%20while%20others%20were%20hit%20by%20sanctions%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20is%20changing%20a%20longtime%20millionaire-friendly%20tax%20policy%20that%20effectively%20allowed%20foreign%20wealth%20to%20be%20earned%20tax%20free.%20The%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20UK%20residents%20who%20qualify%20as%20%26quot%3Bnon-dom%26quot%3B%20filers%20are%20now%20set%20to%20eventually%20pay%20taxes%20on%20their%20foreign%20earnings%2C%20a%20major%20disruption%20for%20the%20wealthy%20elite.%20Alternative%20ports%20of%20call%20for%20this%20group%20of%20millionaires%20will%20likely%20include%20Paris%2C%20Dubai%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20the%20Italian%20Riviera%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fpublications%2Fhenley-private-wealth-migration-report-2024%2Flondons-wealth-exodus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%3C%2Fa%3E%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Netherlands%20also%20similarly%20holds%20an%20outsize%20number%20of%20wealthy%20residents%3A%20over%201.2%20million%20millionaires%2C%20which%20is%20about%20the%20same%20as%20Italy%20and%20Spain%20but%20with%20a%20smaller%20economy%20than%20its%20peers.%20UBS%20forecasts%20the%20country's%20millionaire%20count%20will%20go%20down%204%25%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202013%20to%202023%2C%20the%20Netherlands'%20millionaire%20number%20jumped%2032%25%2C%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20to%20BI%20by%20Andrew%20Amoils%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20New%20World%20Wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20rate%20there%20has%20been%20good%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20%5Bthe%5D%20UK%2C%26quot%3B%20Amoils%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeopolitical%20instability%20in%20Europe%2C%20marked%20by%20the%20rise%20of%20far-right%20parties%20and%20potential%20conflicts%2C%20has%20made%20wealthy%20individuals%20seek%20alternative%20residence%20options%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-buy-citizenship-golden-passport-countries-list-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20migration%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20applications%20have%20spiked%20nearly%2060%25%20for%20such%20programs%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Henley%20and%20Partners%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20These%20programs%20offer%20residence%20rights%20or%20citizenship%20in%20exchange%20for%20significant%20financial%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuk-netherlands-how-many-millionaires-moving-taxes-politics-nondom-ubs-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721193079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669752585439fb59cebdfafd