nning%20our%20routes.%20We%20choose%20a%20starting%20point%20and%20an%20endpoint%2C%20then%20look%20for%20significant%20landmarks%20or%20places%20of%20interest%20along%20the%20way.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20travelling%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20we%20included%20stops%20at%20significant%20sites%20like%20the%2023%20Temples%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%20of%20India%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Save%20cost%20by%20budgeting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBudgeting%20for%20long-distance%20bike%20trips%20involves%20major%20expenses%20like%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20and%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFuel%20costs%20are%20fixed%2C%20but%20we%20save%20on%20food%20and%20accommodation.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20stayed%20in%20budget%20hotels%20for%20as%20low%20as%20%E2%82%B9400%2C%20though%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20suitable%20when%20travelling%20with%20my%20partner.%20We%20prefer%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F145039%2Fnews-maharashtra-airbnb-village-life%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20booking%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20safer%20and%20sometimes%20cheaper%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22He%20has%20travelled%20over%2060%2C000%20km%20on%20his%20bike%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-500x262.jp