es%20and%20humidity%20of%2060%20to%2065%20percent.%20These%20parameters%20can%20be%20different%20for%20Kashmir.%20We%20need%20to%20first%20analyse%20the%20geography%2C%20climate%2C%20and%20weather%20conditions%2C%20and%20accordingly%20design%20and%20set%20up%20the%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Pritpal%20also%20started%20Farmcult%2C%20a%20bootstrapped%20Agritech%20startup%20providing%20end-to-end%20solutions%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20hydroponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmcult%20currently%20operates%20under%20two%20business%20models%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%3A%20%3Cstrong%3ETurnkey%20Projects%20and%20Consulting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Farmcult%20designs%20and%20sets%20up%20modern%C2%A0%20hydroponic%20farms%2C%20customised%20according%20to%20the%20geographical%20location%20and%20the%20crop%20to%20be%20cultivated.%20They%20not%20only%20set%20up%20the%20farms%2C%20but%20also%20support%20their%20clients%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%2C%20ensuring%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20hydroponics%20business.%20Farmcult%20also%20helps%20establish%20market%20linkages%20for%20the%20crops%20being%20cultivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritpal%20aspires%20to%20encourage%20more%20people%20to%20adopt%20hydroponics.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-2-1721052208-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356983%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPritpal%20aspires%20to%20encourage%20more%20people%20to%20adopt%20hydroponics.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20%3Cstrong%3EPassive%20Income%20Model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20For%20clients%20who%20intend%20to%20start%20a%20large-scale%20hydroponics%20business%20but%20lack%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20manage%20the%20farms%2C%20Farmcult%20offers%20comprehensive%20support.%20They%20not%20only%20help%20set%20up%20the%20farm%20but%20also%20manage%20daily%20operations%2C%20right%20from%20germination%20to%20harvesting%20and%20market%20linkages.%20Farmcult%20shares%20quarterly%20returns%20with%20clients%20who%20have%20invested%20in%20the%20farm.%20Pritpal%20says%20that%20they%20are%20currently%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20people%20for%20this%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmcult%20also%20provides%20workshops%20and%20training%20to%20the%20community%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20hydroponic%20farming%2C%20including%20sustainability%2C%20water%20efficiency%2C%20and%20chemical-free%20produce.%20They%20have%20trained%20more%20than%20100%20people%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdit%20Bhatia%2C%20who%20trained%20under%20Pritpal%20last%20April%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnyone%20can%20practise%20hydroponics%20farming.%20It%20is%20very%20useful%20for%20crops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20where%20the%20growth%20cycle%20reduces%20from%2090%20to%2040%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFormal%20training%20becomes%20essential%20in%20hydroponics%20to%20get%20maximum%20yield%20and%20return%20on%20investment.%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20maintain%20water%20temperature%20and%20control%20humidity%20levels.