1178.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356495%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%2C%20the%20first%20biggest%20transformation%20with%20this%20setup%20was%20to%20have%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20grid-backed%20setfup%20was%20different%20from%20a%20net-metered%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%2C%20Suneet%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20net-metered%20system%2C%20you%20do%20not%20require%20to%20store%20the%20energy%20and%20feed%20excess%20energy%20to%20the%20grid%20and%20get%20it%20back%20from%20it%20when%20you%20are%20not%20generating%20enough%20power.%20It%20is%20a%20more%20economical%20way%20for%20harnessing%20solar%20energy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20we%20do%20not%20feed%20excess%20power%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20instead%20store%20the%20excess%20energy%20and%20use%20it%20during%20non-generation%20hours%2C%20say%20during%20the%20nights%20and%20cloudy%20days.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20backup.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20am%20dependent%20on%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%20coal-backed%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20major%20production%20of%20electricity%20is%20achieved%20through%20coal%20thermal%20power%20plants%20which%20is%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F