01%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20planned%20a%20grid%20backed%20solar%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20system%20in%20the%20house%20with%20a%2015%20kWp%20capacity.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20only%20I%20was%20convinced%20about%20this%20setup%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20keep%20the%20grid%20as%20a%20backup.%20We%20have%20programmed%20the%20system%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20firstly%20it%20consumes%20the%20solar%20power%2C%20then%20it%20takes%20power%20from%20batteries%20during%20non-generation%20hours.%20If%20the%20battery%20ever%20drops%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20take%20power%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20which%20hardly%20happens.%20The%20entire%20system%20works%20seamlessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%2010%20months%20a%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20claims%20to%20use%20zero%20energy%20from%20the%20grid.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20consume%20some%20energy%20from%20the%20grid%20for%20about%20two%20months%20in%20the%20summer%20when%20we%20have%20to%20run%20the%20air%20conditioner%20by%20the%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20generation%20in%20the%20day%20to%20run%20the%20AC%20at%20all%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20end%20up%20having%20Rs%201%2C500-Rs%202%2C000%20bills%20in%20those%20months%2C%20of%20which%20the%20fixed%20metre%20charge%20is%20about%20Rs%20500%20to%20700%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20setup%20cost%20the%20couple%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20they%20believe%20they%20would%20get%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20limitations%20of%20the%20entire%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20Shilpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20running%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20the%20mixer%2C%20water%20pumps%20only%20in%20the%20solar%20hours%20between%2010am%20to%20