na%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356150%2Fhuman-animal-conflict-without-harm-bengaluru-engineer-tech-katidhan-startup-shark-tank%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forget%20To%20Take%20Your%20Meds%3F%2015-YO%20Designed%20Mini%20Robot%20To%20Help%20His%20Grandparents%20%26amp%3B%20Wowed%20UNICEF!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20having%20a%20friend%20who%E2%80%99d%20nudge%20you%20every%20time%20you%20needed%20to%20take%20your%20medicine%20dose.%20They%E2%80%99d%20organise%20your%20pills%2C%20hand%20them%20to%20you%20and%20with%20it%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20to%20make%20things%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cool%20thought%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20a%20Class%2011%20student%20at%20Navrachana%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Vadodara%20has%20innovated%3B%20albeit%20his%20creation%20is%20a%20miniaturised%2C%20robotic%20version%20of%20the%20said%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Meditel%E2%80%99%2C%20as%2015-year-old%20Nikhil%20Lemos%20has%20christened%20his%20brainchild%2C%20was%20born%20out%20of%20an%20innocent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330982%2Faditya-chaudhury-builds-neurosight-vaccivan-and-kalam-startup-to-help-student-innovators-with-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20to%20help%20his%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20how%20they%20would%20sometimes%20forget%20to%20take%20their%20pills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20ideate%2C%20a%20young%20Nikhil%20put%20pen%20to%20paper%20and%20sketched%20what%20he%20assumed%20would%20be%20a%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20an%20alarm%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20was%20it%3B%20a%20doodle%20on%20the%20last%20page%20of%20a%20notebook.%20But%20a%20science%20fair%20at%20the%20end%20of%20term%20had%20him%20revisit%20this%20doodle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20innovative%20and%20I%20thought%20of%20going%20back%20to%20this%20idea.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20Meditel%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20innovation%20has%20grown%20with%20Nikhil%3B%20the%20two%20have%20shared%20a%20parallel%20journey%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20transcended%20from%20being%20a%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20to%20a%20paper%20model%20to%20a%20basic%20prototype.%20From%20there%20it%20transformed%20into%20a%20full-blown%20electrical%20model%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20nuances%20Nikhil%20found%20himself%20explaining%20to%20none%20other%20than%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20has%20been%20dream-like.%20And%20in%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Nikhil%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-A